Directory r3broot/macros/r3b/califa contents:

 TUM/     	      macros for iPhos simulation, see README in the directory

 auto/                macros for automatization the simulation of the BARREL

 s438/                directory for experiment s438 macros and results

 README		      This file


 		      	     SIMULATION PART

 runsim.C	      single macro for running the CALIFA simulation
                      usage: set your parameters at the beginning of the macro and run it
                             with root, either directly ('root -l runsim.C') or inside the 
                             root sesion ('root [0] .L runsim.C , root [1] runsim(nEvents)')

 r3bsim.C	      configuration macro for running the simulation in R3BRoot; based on 
                      macro 'r3ball.C' from directory r3broot/macros/r3b

 califaEventDisplay.C macro for starting the CALIFA event viewer

 checkResults.C	      example macro with analysis and visualization for the results of the 
 		      CsI BARREL and CsI Forward End Cap simulation. It should 
		      be configured in the SETTINGS section within the macro. 

 califaAna.C          macro for starting the CALIFA hit finder task (if not started when
                      launching the simulation

 califaAnaCal.C       macro for starting the CALIFA calibration task 


